| Principle | Application |
|-----------|-------------|
| **Single Responsibility** | Each class has one reason to change |
| **Open/Closed** | Easy to add new discount types, tax rules, or notification channels |
| **Liskov Substitution** | All discount/tax/notification implementations are interchangeable |
